description:
Gabe was abandoned by his mother at the age of 3 on the streets of Calcutta, and was later adopted by an American couple.. Gabe always seemed happy in the USA, but kept a feeling deep inside that he was an outsider. He started to rebel in high school and resented his Christian upbringing. He delved into using marijuana and cocaine, and soon turned to heroine. He supported his drug habit with an insurance payoff of $37,500 from a car accident. His adoptive parents feel he needs an intervention now, or his addiction and depression will kill him.
